<plot>Strings tells the story of a troubled pianist, Billy, who gets involved with a group of vigilantes fronting as an experimental therapy group. When Billy commits to joining their group and leaving his old life behind, he finds his new identity comes with a price if he attempts to return home. After a botched job, Billy must make the ultimate sacrifice as he is forced to undergo facial reconstructive surgery to avoid being identified and putting the rest of the group at risk. Years later, he returns to his old life to check on the wife he left behind. But returning comes with a price when those responsible for Billy's face change find out he's broken their only rule.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?518540</url></doc>
